name: footnote
text: Top 5 modalities across all CSIC participants. May differ from top 5 modalities for WakemedLow usability for MTBF because all assets require at least 1 CM event for MTBF calculation, and most assets require at least 2 CM events% WOs with matching asset = 1 - % orphaned work orders. Orphaned work orders = work orders whose asset ID is not found in the asset datasetOrphaned work orders don’t have a matching asset, so the asset’s modality is unknown. % orphaned work orders and % of WOs with matching assets cannot be calculated for a subset of modalities / makes / models
